{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/559130/extras/IV11.gif?t=1728310888\" /><br><br>Tune yourself to the voices lurking in the head of John Blake - the tormented man dwelling in a trap\u2026 that only you can guide him out of. <br><br>You start your adventure by waking up in an unknown place, not remembering what happened and how you got there. Your only companion is a mystery voice that guides you through a previously unknown world and what\u2019s more, is the only main factor that can reveal your past. <br><br><strong>Inner Voices</strong> is an adventure game with a <strong>non-linear plot, procedurally generated user path</strong> and (more than) a pinch of the <strong>atmosphere of your favorite horrors. </strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/559130/extras/IV22.gif?t=1728310888\" /><br><br>To find out more about John Blake\u2019s past, you will need to solve various logic puzzles and the only way to regain the memories is to follow the unknown voice in your head. You will be constantly searching for a way to escape the randomised maze of rooms, you will be haunted by new voices and you will be the one deciding\u2026 <i>who dies.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/559130/extras/IV33.gif?t=1728310888\" /><br><br><strong>WHAT IS SO UNIQUE ABOUT INNER VOICES?</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Non-linear storyline</strong> full of plot twists and choices, that may lead you to <strong>5 different endings</strong>.<br></li><li> Intriguing, disquieting gameplay due to the <strong>ever-changing randomized maze</strong>.<br></li><li> <strong>Unique, dark atmosphere</strong> inspired by the works of H. P. Lovecraft, E. A. Poe and S. King.<br></li><li> A climatic experience thanks to the <strong>moody soundtrack</strong> and audio design.<b